Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.36,中文,,0,0,0,,替我向莎拉问好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.35,中文,,0,0,0,,多处撕裂伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:11.94,中文,,0,0,0,,看看我女儿,她才五岁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:30.00,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.88,中文,,0,0,0,,没事了,这里是医院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:37.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你身上痛吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:40.43,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以给你注射止痛药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:44.89,中文,,0,0,0,,艾莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.77,中文,,0,0,0,,艾莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.56,中文,,0,0,0,,好了,艾莉,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:54.23,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好了 - 艾莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.53,中文,,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:08.98,中文,,0,0,0,,最后生还者第二季 第3集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:25.58,中文,,0,0,0,,(三个月后)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:04.20,中文,,0,0,0,,一到十级,你的疼痛有几级?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.74,中文,,0,0,0,,不疼,零级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.79,中文,,0,0,0,,零级,已经很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.37,中文,,0,0,0,,来吧,最后一次肺功能检查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.13,中文,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:21.09,中文,,0,0,0,,挺好的,就是今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.59,中文,,0,0,0,,- 那我可以... - 就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:26.14,中文,,0,0,0,,你还得见一个人,然后就能出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我的老天爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.10,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗? - 挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:38.52,中文,,0,0,0,,回答这么快就是不好的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:39.82,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧,再问我一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:41.98,中文,,0,0,0,,艾莉,你好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:47.62,中文,,0,0,0,,让我想想,这事很复杂 毕竟感觉这东西...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:48.83,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:51.33,中文,,0,0,0,,拜托,我一直被困在这里,自从...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:07:00.04,中文,,0,0,0,,没错,我想他 他对我来说很重要,我既伤心又难过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.71,中文,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.76,中文,,0,0,0,,但我好奇的是跨年夜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:09.22,中文,,0,0,0,,你们两个在舞会上吵架了 那是你最后一次和他说话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:13.85,中文,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我回家时,他站在门廊上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:22.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我该跟他聊聊的,但我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:26.03,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你后悔吗? - 当然后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:30.66,中文,,0,0,0,,但你和一个人最后相处的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.70,中文,,0,0,0,,不能定义你们整体的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.37,中文,,0,0,0,,道理是这个道理,但事实往往如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.63,中文,,0,0,0,,在我和乔尔相处的最后时光里 他曾说...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.80,中文,,0,0,0,,他对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.01,中文,,0,0,0,,可能很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.35,中文,,0,0,0,,他说他干什么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.93,中文,,0,0,0,,问题就在这儿,他的话前后不搭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.81,中文,,0,0,0,,他说“我救了她”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.27,中文,,0,0,0,,他救过我很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:05.32,中文,,0,0,0,,对,换我也会这么想 但那不算“对不起”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.28,中文,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:10.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道他什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我没觉得他对不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:20.50,中文,,0,0,0,,不管他说的是什么 真希望我能放过他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:26.17,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我只能放过自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:29.68,中文,,0,0,0,,你做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.39,中文,,0,0,0,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:36.35,中文,,0,0,0,,如果人人都像你这么健康 我还怎么换取大麻和酒啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.52,中文,,0,0,0,,不用担心,这镇上还有很多操蛋的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.85,中文,,0,0,0,,对,但你不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:14.51,中文,,0,0,0,,(米勒)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:24.65,中文,,0,0,0,,(乔尔,谢谢你做的一切)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:41.39,中文,,0,0,0,,艾莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:46.64,中文,,0,0,0,,妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:52.98,中文,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:10.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我去医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.37,中文,,0,0,0,,他们什么时候让你出院的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:16.09,中文,,0,0,0,,- 30分钟前 - 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.71,中文,,0,0,0,,他们让我见盖尔了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我从来没说...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:30.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你来看了我那么多次 我早该说谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:33.44,中文,,0,0,0,,不用客气 换我住院,你也会来看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.98,中文,,0,0,0,,- 对,也许不会那么频繁 - 是啊,可能不会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我做了饼干给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.86,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.45,中文,,0,0,0,,算是一份和解礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.62,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我要让你生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.42,中文,,0,0,0,,在医院里...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.30,中文,,0,0,0,,你曾问过我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.55,中文,,0,0,0,,那天的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:04.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我说我没听到任何有用的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.39,中文,,0,0,0,,其实我没说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:13.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道他们大部分人的名字 也知道他们是哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.81,中文,,0,0,0,,你听我说完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:18.44,中文,,0,0,0,,- 医生叫我不要让你太激动 - 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:21.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道我一旦说出他们在哪 你会拔掉输液管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.45,中文,,0,0,0,,爬也要爬过去找他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:29.70,中文,,0,0,0,,你浪费了我们的时间 你让他们逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.75,中文,,0,0,0,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:37.38,中文,,0,0,0,,几个星期以来 这镇上一片狼藉,到处都是葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.71,中文,,0,0,0,,没人会去追杀任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.01,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我突然想到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:44.72,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你想找一个人 而你只知道对方最终的目的地...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:49.14,中文,,0,0,0,,还不如让对方先到了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我也爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.32,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧,我们先说名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.61,中文,,0,0,0,,那个黑发男叫曼尼 另一个男的叫欧文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:48.32,中文,,0,0,0,,黑发女孩和光头女孩里有一个叫诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:50.70,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我不确定是哪个 - 那个扎辫子的女孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:52.83,中文,,0,0,0,,艾比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:54.45,中文,,0,0,0,,艾比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.04,中文,,0,0,0,,他们来自什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:01.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我在一个背包上看到了一块布章
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.13,中文,,0,0,0,,黄色三角,有个狼头...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.47,中文,,0,0,0,,还有三个字母,WLF
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:12.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我记得尤金给我讲过 他还在火萤时的一个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:15.31,中文,,0,0,0,,他说有些地区性小团体 都想对抗联邦救灾局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.23,中文,,0,0,0,,还说他们没有联合起来真够蠢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:22.36,中文,,0,0,0,,其中一个团体就是华盛顿解放阵线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.11,中文,,0,0,0,,来自西雅图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.32,中文,,0,0,0,,WLF,狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.61,中文,,0,0,0,,一群傻逼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.12,中文,,0,0,0,,- 他有说这个团体有多小吗? - 没说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:35.45,中文,,0,0,0,,不过,既然从那以后没人提过他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:37.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我猜应该是我们能应付的小团体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.04,中文,,0,0,0,,还有谁知道这事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:42.67,中文,,0,0,0,,就我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我没打算在告诉你之前告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:07.86,中文,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:22.96,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我得考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:27.71,中文,,0,0,0,,考虑什么?我们去干掉那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.80,中文,,0,0,0,,艾莉,事情没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.63,中文,,0,0,0,,小镇还在恢复中,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.97,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我们明白你的出发点 - 不,我们不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:38.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我不明白,如果死的人是你 乔尔早在天亮前就赶往西雅图了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:41.27,中文,,0,0,0,,他那么做一定是为了救我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.90,中文,,0,0,0,,可我们现在有伤亡,还不能走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.98,中文,,0,0,0,,换他也会崩溃的 他会把一切责任揽到自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:49.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我见过很多次了,别以为我不了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.45,中文,,0,0,0,,他是我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:18:00.79,中文,,0,0,0,,听着,我不是说你不该去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.21,中文,,0,0,0,,但是既然要组队 就得组一支像样的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.88,中文,,0,0,0,,把这件事告诉玛丽亚 没错,必须告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.80,中文,,0,0,0,,她会召开议会,通知全镇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:13.05,中文,,0,0,0,,每个想发声的人都能发声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.68,中文,,0,0,0,,但你会支持我们的,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:17.43,中文,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.23,中文,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.53,中文,,0,0,0,,还有你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:33.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你要是再有事瞒着我 就去最累的岗位上待一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.45,中文,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.50,中文,,0,0,0,,还有,艾莉...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:47.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我们把死者埋在镇南十英里的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:49.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以去看他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:54.55,中文,,0,0,0,,去西雅图的时候再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:11.48,中文,,0,0,0,,(普吉特步道 植物园,西雅图步道)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:52.90,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:57.95,中文,,0,0,0,,没人跟来,很安全,继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.07,中文,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:02.12,中文,,0,0,0,,等我们重新安顿好 我们会教你吹口哨的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么不能告诉我目的地是哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.46,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我们还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我已经说了我们要去的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:16.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道,但她为什么不能保护我们?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.09,中文,,0,0,0,,先知?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:23.43,中文,,0,0,0,,她十年前就死了,康斯坦丝 我可不会指望她帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:26.18,中文,,0,0,0,,但艾斯拉说先知是永生的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:29.06,中文,,0,0,0,,从某种角度看没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:31.10,中文,,0,0,0,,但先知不是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:32.56,中文,,0,0,0,,他们只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.82,中文,,0,0,0,,能看到别人看不到的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:37.40,中文,,0,0,0,,并且不计代价分享真相的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:40.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的先知也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.12,中文,,0,0,0,,- 没错 - 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就是这样让她的精神永存的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:49.71,中文,,0,0,0,,遵循她的话语,服从她的教诲 同时保护自己的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.71,中文,,0,0,0,,那能给我一把锤子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.34,中文,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.39,中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我,你觉得更安全了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:08.02,中文,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.60,中文,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.77,中文,,0,0,0,,要知道,我们现在给你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:15.44,中文,,0,0,0,,会比锤子给你更多的安全感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:18.90,中文,,0,0,0,,那就是出离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:21.82,中文,,0,0,0,,出离家乡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.49,中文,,0,0,0,,出离战争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:36.30,中文,,0,0,0,,找掩护!快!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:54.56,中文,,0,0,0,,是恶魔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:57.65,中文,,0,0,0,,是狼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.91,中文,,0,0,0,,很好,注意旋转,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:07.62,中文,,0,0,0,,现在换右边,只打右边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:10.25,中文,,0,0,0,,- 这边伤害更大 - 我注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:11.91,中文,,0,0,0,,- 来吧 - 好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:17.29,中文,,0,0,0,,用力点!坚持住!最后五拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:24.01,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好了,今天到此为止 - 好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.89,0:22:26.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.39,中文,,0,0,0,,一个无所事事三个月的人能做成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:31.27,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得很惊喜 - 是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:32.39,中文,,0,0,0,,平时做俯卧撑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:34.39,中文,,0,0,0,,对,还在他们不注意时卷腹了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:38.61,中文,,0,0,0,,这样就行了 再过几周,你就能恢复原来的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:40.11,中文,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:43.61,中文,,0,0,0,,- 也就是你该有的水平的八成 - 随便了,去你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:50.49,中文,,0,0,0,,听说你加入议会了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:52.12,中文,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:54.62,中文,,0,0,0,,那你肯定知道接下来的会议
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:22:58.29,中文,,0,0,0,,没错,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:01.51,中文,,0,0,0,,我能指望你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.22,0:23:05.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我不能讨论即将开始的投票
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:08.43,中文,,0,0,0,,- 搞什么?是我啊 - 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:10.93,中文,,0,0,0,,老兄,当时你也在场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:12.35,中文,,0,0,0,,这我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:14.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.10,0:23:17.27,中文,,0,0,0,,老天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:20.15,中文,,0,0,0,,艾莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:23.86,中文,,0,0,0,,听完大家的意见,议会才能作决定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.99,0:23:25.99,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我给你一点建议
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:29.99,中文,,0,0,0,,把你的想法整理清楚、写下来 明天念给大家听
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.12,0:23:33.87,中文,,0,0,0,,- 知道了,因为我很蠢 - 因为你愤怒,艾莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:36.58,中文,,0,0,0,,没人会投票给愤怒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:48.47,中文,,0,0,0,,...所以我一直说我们要多投资火鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:49.80,中文,,0,0,0,,少投资鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:53.27,中文,,0,0,0,,这就要说回我之前对玉米的看法了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.39,0:23:57.06,中文,,0,0,0,,有些人听我这么说过 玉米不是最容易种植的作物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.19,0:23:59.19,中文,,0,0,0,,但它是生长最快的作物之一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:03.82,中文,,0,0,0,,你们可以绘一张图 把收成时间和所需资源以及难易度...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:07.53,中文,,0,0,0,,斯考特,抱歉打断你,不要偏题
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.99,中文,,0,0,0,,这是公开会议,章程上说...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.12,0:24:14.20,中文,,0,0,0,,或许我们应该回到 大家原本要讨论的议程上来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.83,0:24:17.21,中文,,0,0,0,,我对西雅图的事没意见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.33,0:24:19.04,中文,,0,0,0,,好,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:23.63,中文,,0,0,0,,斯考特说完了,接下来是瑞秋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:26.88,中文,,0,0,0,,乔尔对我们很多人来说非常重要...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.01,0:24:28.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我听不见,大声点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.84,0:24:31.55,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你能帮我抱着他吗? - 好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.39,0:24:33.68,中文,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.77,0:24:43.61,中文,,0,0,0,,我说乔尔对我们很多人来说非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.90,0:24:46.07,中文,,0,0,0,,但他并非唯一一个重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.15,0:24:48.95,中文,,0,0,0,,那天我失去了我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.99,0:24:52.20,中文,,0,0,0,,这里很多人都埋葬了家人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.32,0:24:55.62,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你们要派去16个顶尖成员?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.58,0:25:00.21,中文,,0,0,0,,他们不在的时候,如果掠夺者来了 谁去墙上抵御他们?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.33,0:25:02.13,中文,,0,0,0,,墙还没修好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.79,0:25:05.88,中文,,0,0,0,,而且谁也不能保证 那16个人都能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.51,0:25:10.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我同情你们,汤米和艾莉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.43,0:25:13.76,中文,,0,0,0,,但我们伤亡惨重,现在出击太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.14,0:25:16.22,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你,瑞秋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.73,0:25:22.10,中文,,0,0,0,,下一位是卡莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.61,0:25:29.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我长话短说,毕竟这是个简单的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.78,0:25:31.99,中文,,0,0,0,,有人来我们这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.95,0:25:33.95,中文,,0,0,0,,杀了乔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.91,0:25:37.45,中文,,0,0,0,,我们为什么不想复仇?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.20,0:25:41.21,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我们不该那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.75,0:25:45.42,中文,,0,0,0,,宽恕他人,方能被人宽恕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.13,0:25:49.13,中文,,0,0,0,,放下怨恨和仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.26,0:25:53.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我都不是基督徒 可我一直觉得这么做很明智
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.72,0:25:57.97,中文,,0,0,0,,这正是我们与掠夺者和杀人犯 不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.10,0:26:00.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我们懂得仁慈
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.39,0:26:04.06,中文,,0,0,0,,那些混蛋不配得到我们的仁慈
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.52,0:26:07.77,中文,,0,0,0,,当然不配,所以才叫仁慈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.90,0:26:09.23,中文,,0,0,0,,去你的屁话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.24,0:26:12.11,中文,,0,0,0,,你能这么说,也不是什么好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.24,0:26:13.24,中文,,0,0,0,,- 赛斯,坐下 - 不
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.36,0:26:14.82,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你不在发言名单上 - 不!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.41,0:26:17.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我们到底在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.62,0:26:20.95,中文,,0,0,0,,哎呦,太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.08,0:26:24.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要原谅每一个 骑在我们头上拉屎的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.17,0:26:27.42,中文,,0,0,0,,他们闯进了我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.54,0:26:29.38,中文,,0,0,0,,抓走了我们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.05,0:26:31.13,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.26,0:26:34.51,中文,,0,0,0,,有人射杀了你们的兄弟 你们还想把门锁拆了?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.63,0:26:35.89,中文,,0,0,0,,幼稚!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.60,0:26:38.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你们这些白痴,他们还会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.56,0:26:42.77,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我们没让他们付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.89,0:26:45.40,中文,,0,0,0,,等他们回来时,一定带着嘲笑的嘴脸
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.52,0:26:48.86,中文,,0,0,0,,而你们都活该
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.53,0:26:51.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你们这群...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.24,0:26:53.99,中文,,0,0,0,,该死的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.16,0:27:05.87,中文,,0,0,0,,(斯考特、瑞秋、卡莱尔、艾莉)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.46,0:27:09.50,中文,,0,0,0,,艾莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.36,0:27:31.15,中文,,0,0,0,,“我通常不会准备发言稿”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.27,0:27:33.61,中文,,0,0,0,,“因为我向来有话直说,不假思索”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.74,0:27:36.74,中文,,0,0,0,,“这让我惹上了不少麻烦”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.86,0:27:40.24,中文,,0,0,0,,“让我付出了无法挽回的代价”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.95,0:27:45.58,中文,,0,0,0,,“但我这次输不起 因为我知道我的要求很过分”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.25,0:27:49.17,中文,,0,0,0,,“我要我们在最糟的时机”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.29,0:27:51.25,中文,,0,0,0,,“拿更多的人力和资源去冒险”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.38,0:27:55.34,中文,,0,0,0,,“我想告诉大家 我想要的并非复仇”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.47,0:27:57.80,中文,,0,0,0,,“真的,这跟复仇无关”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.93,0:28:00.26,中文,,0,0,0,,“我要的是 你们过去给予他人的东西”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.68,0:28:02.97,中文,,0,0,0,,“我要正义”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.56,0:28:07.56,中文,,0,0,0,,“因为除此之外 就只剩沉默与放弃了”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.14,0:28:12.40,中文,,0,0,0,,“而外面的人 也只会默默地放弃我们”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.52,0:28:15.19,中文,,0,0,0,,“如果我或你们遭遇不幸”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.32,0:28:18.15,中文,,0,0,0,,“全世界没有人愿意动一动手指”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.70,0:28:21.49,中文,,0,0,0,,“我们有专门的词称呼这种人”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.33,0:28:24.12,中文,,0,0,0,,“那就是‘陌生人’”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.24,0:28:26.91,中文,,0,0,0,,“我觉得我们之间不是陌生人”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.04,0:28:29.46,中文,,0,0,0,,“我得知道我能依靠你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.58,0:28:33.38,中文,,0,0,0,,“我发誓 如果有人伤害你们或你们爱的人”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.50,0:28:35.00,中文,,0,0,0,,“你们也可以依靠我”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.63,0:28:37.47,中文,,0,0,0,,“这才是我们的凝聚力”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.26,0:28:41.34,中文,,0,0,0,,“不是聚餐,也不是跨年舞会”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.18,0:28:45.01,中文,,0,0,0,,“更不是一堵墙 因为那堵墙已经被撞破了”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.14,0:28:47.02,中文,,0,0,0,,“而杰克逊依然挺立”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.31,0:28:52.36,中文,,0,0,0,,“我会接受议会的一切决议”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.48,0:28:55.61,中文,,0,0,0,,“但我拜托你们”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.82,0:28:59.61,中文,,0,0,0,,“不惜一切代价伸张正义”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.28,0:29:02.37,中文,,0,0,0,,“不是为了我”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.37,0:29:04.58,中文,,0,0,0,,“甚至不是为了乔尔”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.74,0:29:10.83,中文,,0,0,0,,“我拜托你们为我们大家这么做”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.80,0:29:16.80,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.39,0:29:31.31,中文,,0,0,0,,议会将就派遣16名成员前往西雅图
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.44,0:29:34.94,中文,,0,0,0,,寻找并处决杀害乔尔之人的提案 进行投票
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.38,0:29:58.38,中文,,0,0,0,,艾米贝丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.18,0:30:04.18,中文,,0,0,0,,“赞成”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.22,0:30:07.22,中文,,0,0,0,,“反对”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.93,0:30:09.93,中文,,0,0,0,,“赞成”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.48,0:30:13.52,中文,,0,0,0,,“反对”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.27,0:30:16.27,中文,,0,0,0,,“反对”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.73,0:30:18.73,中文,,0,0,0,,“赞成”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.61,0:30:21.61,中文,,0,0,0,,“反对”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.95,0:30:24.95,中文,,0,0,0,,“反对”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.37,0:30:27.37,中文,,0,0,0,,“反对”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.91,0:30:29.91,中文,,0,0,0,,“反对”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.00,0:30:33.00,中文,,0,0,0,,“反对”
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.13,0:30:39.80,中文,,0,0,0,,八票反对,三票赞成,提案被否决了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.59,0:30:46.68,中文,,0,0,0,,休庭
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.29,0:31:14.41,中文,,0,0,0,,加油,九号球员
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.62,0:31:18.92,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好了,盯紧球! - 快!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.04,0:31:21.92,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好样的,九号! - 加油,罗德尼,冲啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.05,0:31:23.76,中文,,0,0,0,,- 该死 - 他没事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.88,0:31:25.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你是球迷
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.34,0:31:29.22,中文,,0,0,0,,当然,我当年可买过老虎队的季票呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.47,0:31:33.60,中文,,0,0,0,,这其实跟2003年的球队差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.52,0:31:38.27,中文,,0,0,0,,要喝啤酒吗?我跟马歇尔拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.53,0:31:54.08,中文,,0,0,0,,今天开会时,我在人群中看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.41,0:31:56.41,中文,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.58,0:31:59.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我心想
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.96,0:32:02.38,中文,,0,0,0,,“她过去几周可能特别忙”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.38,0:32:04.76,中文,,0,0,0,,太残忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.88,0:32:09.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我自己都该去看心理医生 消化发生的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.14,0:32:10.14,中文,,0,0,0,,可这里没有别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.76,0:32:14.14,中文,,0,0,0,,- 那你怎么办? - 我是个酒鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.27,0:32:16.52,中文,,0,0,0,,而且我尽可能地多抽大麻
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.64,0:32:18.48,中文,,0,0,0,,真是一场大灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.27,0:32:21.40,中文,,0,0,0,,但你来找我不是因为担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.02,0:32:24.53,中文,,0,0,0,,两人出局了,各位,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.65,0:32:25.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.53,0:32:30.07,中文,,0,0,0,,你能看到别人看不到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.16,0:32:34.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我担心她会做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.99,0:32:37.66,中文,,0,0,0,,- 怎么,你不相信她的发言? - 你相信吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.79,0:32:39.54,中文,,0,0,0,,当然不信,她是个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.29,0:32:42.63,中文,,0,0,0,,撒谎的人不一定是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.75,0:32:45.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道,她就是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.05,0:32:48.63,中文,,0,0,0,,她可能只跟一个人说过实话 而他已经...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.76,0:32:53.64,中文,,0,0,0,,但我们可以在这一点上各持己见
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.22,0:33:00.23,中文,,0,0,0,,问题是你很害怕,那我们谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.10,0:33:02.19,中文,,0,0,0,,不收钱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.19,0:33:08.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是不想看她步乔尔的后尘
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.32,0:33:13.74,中文,,0,0,0,,他满口的正当理由
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.83,0:33:18.25,中文,,0,0,0,,其实只是在宣泄而已
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.87,0:33:21.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得她的行为可能是跟他学的?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.55,0:33:29.67,中文,,0,0,0,,其实后天教养的作用微乎其微 其余的都是天性
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.55,0:33:33.14,中文,,0,0,0,,就算她走上某条路 那也不是乔尔教她的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.47,0:33:35.97,中文,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.10,0:33:39.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们一开始就是并肩而行
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.94,0:33:44.23,中文,,0,0,0,,汤米,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.06,0:33:48.11,中文,,0,0,0,,现在她归你管了,你想帮她避开麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.23,0:33:51.11,中文,,0,0,0,,作为从业40年的心理医生 我劝你一句
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.95,0:33:53.11,中文,,0,0,0,,有些人...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.49,0:33:59.83,中文,,0,0,0,,有些人无法拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.27,0:34:30.49,中文,,0,0,0,,- 是谁? - 迪娜
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.53,0:34:35.41,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.99,0:34:39.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.87,0:34:43.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.50,0:34:49.63,中文,,0,0,0,,就你一个人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.38,0:34:51.51,中文,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.85,0:35:00.85,中文,,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.68,0:35:03.68,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.81,0:35:06.90,中文,,0,0,0,,- 别劝我放弃 - 你以为我是来劝你的?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.90,0:35:10.15,中文,,0,0,0,,说说你的计划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.19,0:35:14.11,中文,,0,0,0,,去西雅图杀死艾比
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.24,0:35:15.40,中文,,0,0,0,,路线呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.95,0:35:18.16,中文,,0,0,0,,西北方
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.28,0:35:22.58,中文,,0,0,0,,这里面都是枪吗?有没有医疗用品?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.00,0:35:26.46,中文,,0,0,0,,你最好别在你规划好的西北路线上
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.58,0:35:29.96,中文,,0,0,0,,崴了脚或发高烧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.09,0:35:31.96,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧,我该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.34,0:35:41.51,中文,,0,0,0,,远离高速,避开城市或聚落
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.64,0:35:43.56,中文,,0,0,0,,第一阶段是穿越国家森林
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.68,0:35:46.89,中文,,0,0,0,,出来后,我们沿蛇河峡谷前进
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.02,0:35:49.86,中文,,0,0,0,,- 然后穿越斯诺夸尔米山口 - 斯诺夸尔米?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.98,0:35:51.90,中文,,0,0,0,,对,斯诺夸尔米
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.53,0:35:55.78,中文,,0,0,0,,从东边接近西雅图 然后根据情况重新做评估
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:58.53,中文,,0,0,0,,带好粮食,轻装上路,但要聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.66,0:36:00.58,中文,,0,0,0,,拿厚外套当床垫,拿夹克当被子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.70,0:36:04.95,中文,,0,0,0,,急救箱、电池和防熊喷雾都带上 你要带什么手枪?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.17,0:36:08.25,中文,,0,0,0,,这是乔尔的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.38,0:36:12.17,中文,,0,0,0,,你打算用这个杀死她
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.30,0:36:14.26,中文,,0,0,0,,- 没错 - 那就留到那时候再用
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.38,0:36:15.84,中文,,0,0,0,,它的速度很慢,后坐力特别强
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.18,0:36:20.85,中文,,0,0,0,,真的吗?你想轰掉你的屁股?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.64,0:36:22.76,中文,,0,0,0,,有人这么劝过我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.26,0:36:25.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我们每人起码得有一百发子弹 加上五十发步枪子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.93,0:36:28.31,中文,,0,0,0,,你想带什么长枪都可以 只要有瞄准镜就行
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.44,0:36:31.19,中文,,0,0,0,,氯片、平底锅 还有帮闪闪保持干燥的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.31,0:36:32.86,中文,,0,0,0,,- 只带闪闪吗? - 对
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.98,0:36:34.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我们共骑一匹马,减少资源
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.82,0:36:38.36,中文,,0,0,0,,其他东西都跟你想的一样,除了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.78,0:36:40.78,中文,,0,0,0,,靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.74,0:36:44.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这双匡威 也尊重你一贯的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.45,0:36:46.54,中文,,0,0,0,,但你不能穿帆布鞋横穿荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.66,0:36:48.92,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我那么做过 - 不能穿帆布鞋,有问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.04,0:36:51.54,中文,,0,0,0,,有一个,我们怎么弄到那么多东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.67,0:36:52.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我认识一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.84,0:36:56.59,中文,,0,0,0,,不是吧,你不会告诉杰西了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.71,0:36:58.80,中文,,0,0,0,,怀俄明队长?没有
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.93,0:37:02.22,中文,,0,0,0,,我喜欢他,但他是个死守规矩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.85,0:37:05.81,中文,,0,0,0,,把你要带的衣服都穿上 口袋里装满子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.93,0:37:09.10,中文,,0,0,0,,其他东西必须装进枪套或背包里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.23,0:37:12.06,中文,,0,0,0,,我们凌晨三点在原来的东门见
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.90,0:37:13.90,中文,,0,0,0,,凌晨三点
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.65,0:37:16.69,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.86,0:37:20.86,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.49,0:37:25.12,中文,,0,0,0,,其实你可以直接问我的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.45,0:37:27.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道你愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.75,0:37:31.75,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.95,0:38:09.95,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我换
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.08,0:38:14.17,中文,,0,0,0,,这把枪更好,跟我换
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.31,0:38:33.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么把它弄出来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.44,0:38:38.57,中文,,0,0,0,,珍宁在马厩值夜班 她理解我们想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.69,0:38:39.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我们想做的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.07,0:38:42.61,中文,,0,0,0,,是你在议会上说“我们”的 不是我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.61,0:38:47.28,中文,,0,0,0,,马鞍袋里都是我偷藏的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.41,0:38:50.87,中文,,0,0,0,,能吃两周的硬面包 绷带、酒精、药物和电池
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.00,0:38:54.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我想跟你们一起去 但我在跨年夜被友军误伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.50,0:38:57.04,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你确定是友军吗? - 天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.17,0:39:01.38,中文,,0,0,0,,在巡逻队经过之前 你们只有十分钟,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.07,0:40:54.70,中文,,0,0,0,,(乔尔米勒)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.20,0:42:57.41,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧,字母F
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.08,0:43:02.79,中文,,0,0,0,,字母F,佛...佛利伍麦克乐团
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.91,0:43:04.16,中文,,0,0,0,,- 不对 - 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.29,0:43:05.87,中文,,0,0,0,,什么叫不对?这是我的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.00,0:43:10.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你的看法是错的 因为弗兰克扎帕真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.01,0:43:14.13,中文,,0,0,0,,好了,字母G
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.22,0:43:17.43,中文,,0,0,0,,- 绿日乐队 - 不,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.64,0:43:25.02,中文,,0,0,0,,奥兹奥斯朋
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.14,0:43:27.27,中文,,0,0,0,,很好,分数加倍
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.40,0:43:30.82,中文,,0,0,0,,L、M、N、O、P
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.94,0:43:33.36,中文,,0,0,0,,你真要让我猜完所有字母吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.99,0:43:39.03,中文,,0,0,0,,不用,我很灵活的 让我想想,换个新话题...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.16,0:43:42.70,中文,,0,0,0,,- 沉默也行 - 有了,你杀的第一个人是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.83,0:43:44.12,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.25,0:43:46.08,中文,,0,0,0,,对,有趣的童年故事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.21,0:43:50.00,中文,,0,0,0,,第一个人死得太离谱 但我可以跟你说说第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.96,0:43:52.05,中文,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.76,0:43:56.13,中文,,0,0,0,,那是我和乔尔来杰克逊之前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.26,0:44:00.55,中文,,0,0,0,,在堪萨斯城 他被一个没比我大几岁的孩子突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.85,0:44:06.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我从后面接近他 举起枪,然后...就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.81,0:44:09.06,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉,艾莉
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.86,0:44:12.98,中文,,0,0,0,,有意思,杀人的是我 你却替我难过?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.94,0:44:15.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我就是这么忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.70,0:44:20.62,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你看到露岩或有遮蔽的地方 记得告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.74,0:44:22.24,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么?天气挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.79,0:44:34.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天,雨来得真快 你怎么知道会这样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.96,0:44:37.17,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我是女巫 - 显然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.45,0:45:03.95,中文,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.95,0:45:05.95,中文,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.55,0:45:24.35,中文,,0,0,0,,不过,我还有个蠢问题
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.06,0:45:35.44,中文,,0,0,0,,和跨年夜有关
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.53,0:45:37.53,中文,,0,0,0,,那个吻
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.07,0:45:45.41,中文,,0,0,0,,好,也没什么,你当时嗑嗨了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.53,0:45:46.99,中文,,0,0,0,,而你醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.12,0:45:49.83,中文,,0,0,0,,对,所以那不能代表什么 你是想问这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.96,0:45:52.88,中文,,0,0,0,,不,这个我知道,我想问的是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.71,0:45:56.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你会给那个吻打几分?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.96,0:46:00.42,中文,,0,0,0,,- 一到十分? - 不
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.05,0:46:05.30,中文,,0,0,0,,拜托,你以前吻过女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.43,0:46:06.89,中文,,0,0,0,,你是同性恋,而我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.60,0:46:10.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是好奇,我想知道我厉不厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.27,0:46:12.27,中文,,0,0,0,,一到十分
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.69,0:46:17.27,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧,六分
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.40,0:46:19.99,中文,,0,0,0,,- 去你的,六分! - 这算不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.11,0:46:21.74,中文,,0,0,0,,真是烂透了!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.86,0:46:23.20,中文,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.32,0:46:25.12,中文,,0,0,0,,郑重声明一下,我不相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.24,0:46:29.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你非要问,我就答了,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.45,0:46:33.42,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以回去找杰西
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.54,0:46:34.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我已经找了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.79,0:46:37.21,中文,,0,0,0,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.10,0:46:51.02,中文,,0,0,0,,他有没有给你一种悲伤的感觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.10,0:46:53.89,中文,,0,0,0,,杰西吗?有
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.31,0:46:57.69,中文,,0,0,0,,他跟你说过原因吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.27,0:47:00.32,中文,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.53,0:47:06.03,中文,,0,0,0,,但我觉得他内心深处就是悲伤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.74,0:47:12.66,中文,,0,0,0,,- 至少我希望是这样 - 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.67,0:47:19.46,中文,,0,0,0,,因为如果不是的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.34,0:47:22.59,中文,,0,0,0,,那就是我的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.51,0:47:29.47,中文,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.47,0:47:31.47,中文,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.40,0:47:42.40,中文,,0,0,0,,艾莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.82,0:47:46.61,中文,,0,0,0,,当时我没那么嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.91,0:47:58.96,中文,,0,0,0,,(植物园,西雅图步道)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.71,0:48:00.75,中文,,0,0,0,,还有多远?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.50,0:48:02.50,中文,,0,0,0,,很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.42,0:48:04.88,中文,,0,0,0,,大约十英里
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.67,0:48:09.14,中文,,0,0,0,,理论上 我们会从城北五号公路附近穿出去
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.66,0:48:29.87,中文,,0,0,0,,他死前正在逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.20,0:48:33.45,中文,,0,0,0,,这是什么符号?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.20,0:48:36.08,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道,我也是第一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.59,0:48:51.64,中文,,0,0,0,,子弹的口径各不相同 应该不是联邦救灾局干的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.72,0:48:54.77,中文,,0,0,0,,迪娜
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.68,0:48:57.68,中文,,0,0,0,,迪娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.78,0:49:08.90,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧? - 那边...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.13,0:50:06.13,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.67,0:50:11.97,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起,我从没有过这种反应
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.72,0:50:16.47,中文,,0,0,0,,- 可能是气味太重 - 而且惨不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.23,0:50:21.64,中文,,0,0,0,,如果这是他们干的...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.27,0:50:24.65,中文,,0,0,0,,如果艾比和她的人能对人干出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.86,0:50:26.86,中文,,0,0,0,,能杀害孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.99,0:50:31.99,中文,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.03,0:50:37.03,中文,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.69,0:51:08.90,中文,,0,0,0,,已经很接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.05,0:51:38.80,中文,,0,0,0,,(警告,接近监控区,联邦救灾局)
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.93,0:51:40.39,中文,,0,0,0,,好安静
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.51,0:51:42.81,中文,,0,0,0,,对,过于安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.31,0:51:45.44,中文,,0,0,0,,柯蒂斯还是毒蛇的台词?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.56,0:51:47.23,中文,,0,0,0,,都有,他们在四部电影里都说过
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.69,0:51:50.69,中文,,0,0,0,,(西雅图,九英里)
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.82,0:51:52.36,中文,,0,0,0,,还有九英里
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.07,0:51:55.11,中文,,0,0,0,,九英里
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.43,0:52:22.01,中文,,0,0,0,,该死的西雅图,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.89,0:52:26.69,中文,,0,0,0,,而且也没人对我们开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.31,0:52:32.11,中文,,0,0,0,,看来狼也没那么多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.40,0:52:35.28,中文,,0,0,0,,马上就要少很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.78,0:52:39.61,中文,,0,0,0,,- 柯蒂斯还是毒蛇的台词? - 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.49,0:52:44.37,中文,,0,0,0,,不,是我自创的 我只是想显得我厉害一点
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.04,0:52:48.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你本来就很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.77,0:53:09.77,中文,,0,0,0,,“曼尼”
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.35,0:53:12.40,中文,,0,0,0,,是我,说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.86,0:53:18.15,中文,,0,0,0,,“我们要前往前进作战基地 三号和五号检查站之间安全吗?”
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.12,0:53:26.83,中文,,0,0,0,,明明叫我盯着六号和八号 现在又问三号和五号
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.29,0:53:29.75,中文,,0,0,0,,“曼尼,听到了吗?”
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.87,0:53:32.79,中文,,0,0,0,,等我一分钟,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.42,0:53:39.88,中文,,0,0,0,,没问题,可以往前走了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.15,0:54:03.16,中文,,0,0,0,,(华盛顿解放阵线)
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.64,0:54:32.77,中文,,0,0,0,,(华盛顿解放阵线)
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.16,0:54:45.16,中文,,0,0,0,,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.16,0:54:46.24,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢观赏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Give Sarah my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.27,英文,,0,0,0,,...multiple lacerations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:12.15,英文,,0,0,0,,My daughter, she's five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:31.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:34.09,英文,,0,0,0,,You're in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.39,英文,,0,0,0,,We can give you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:47.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Ellie! Ellie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:53.94,英文,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.69,英文,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:04.36,英文,,0,0,0,,And how would you rate your pain? Scale of one to ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.32,英文,,0,0,0,,- Nothing. Zero. - Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:08.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Can't ask for much more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:12.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay. One last PFT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.29,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:19.96,英文,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:21.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Today's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.55,英文,,0,0,0,,- So, can I just-- - Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:26.09,英文,,0,0,0,,I just need you to see one more person, then you're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:32.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, for fuck's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:36.31,英文,,0,0,0,,- How are you doing? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.56,英文,,0,0,0,,If you say it that fast, it kind of implies you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:39.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay, ask me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:41.98,英文,,0,0,0,,How are you doing, Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:44.65,英文,,0,0,0,,Give me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:47.66,英文,,0,0,0,,It's really complicated 'cause, you know, feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:51.58,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, man, I've been stuck in here since...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:58.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I miss him. He meant a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.17,英文,,0,0,0,,So, yeah. Upset and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.05,英文,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:04.97,英文,,0,0,0,,But I was actually wondering about New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:07.72,英文,,0,0,0,,You two got into it at the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:09.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Was that the last time you spoke to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:13.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:18.27,英文,,0,0,0,,When I got home, he was on the porch,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:22.02,英文,,0,0,0,,and I should've talked to him, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:26.07,英文,,0,0,0,,- Do you regret that? - Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:32.83,英文,,0,0,0,,But your final moment with someone doesn't define your whole time with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.29,英文,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't, but it often does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.67,英文,,0,0,0,,In my last moment with Joel, he said he
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:42.92,英文,,0,0,0,,wronged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.05,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.43,英文,,0,0,0,,What is it that he said that he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the thing. It didn't really make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.81,英文,,0,0,0,,He said, "I saved her."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:01.86,英文,,0,0,0,,He saved me a lot of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:05.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I would think so. But that's not wronging someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.28,英文,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:10.95,英文,,0,0,0,,No idea what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:14.79,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't feel wronged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Man, I wish I could have let him off the hook
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.54,英文,,0,0,0,,for whatever it was he was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:26.13,英文,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have to let myself off the hook for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, you really are doing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:36.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Shit, if everyone were as healthy as you, what would I do for weed and booze?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.64,英文,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't worry, Gail, there's still a lot of fucked up people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.10,英文,,0,0,0,,- in this town. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.85,英文,,0,0,0,,But not you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.46,英文,,0,0,0,,I went to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:13.33,英文,,0,0,0,,When'd they let you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:16.00,英文,,0,0,0,,- Thirty minutes ago. - Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:18.71,英文,,0,0,0,,They made me talk to Gail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:25.55,英文,,0,0,0,,I never said--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:28.47,英文,,0,0,0,,I should have said thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.39,英文,,0,0,0,,for all those times you came to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.48,英文,,0,0,0,,That's okay. You would have done the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:36.19,英文,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, maybe not as often. - Yeah, no, probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.65,英文,,0,0,0,,I made you cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.70,英文,,0,0,0,,- Just 'cause? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.53,英文,,0,0,0,,This is a peace offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.87,英文,,0,0,0,,Because I'm about to make you angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:55.71,英文,,0,0,0,,In the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:14:00.55,英文,,0,0,0,,when you asked me about that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.39,英文,,0,0,0,,I told you I didn't learn anything useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.68,英文,,0,0,0,,That wasn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:13.73,英文,,0,0,0,,I know most of their names, and I know where they're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:17.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Please, just listen. The doctors told me not to upset you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.82,英文,,0,0,0,,- I don't give a fuck. - And I knew that if I told you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.61,英文,,0,0,0,,where they were, you'd just start pulling your tubes out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.49,英文,,0,0,0,,and crawling on your hands and knees to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.41,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't give a fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:30.20,英文,,0,0,0,,You cost us time. You let them get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.71,英文,,0,0,0,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:37.42,英文,,0,0,0,,this town was wreckage and funerals for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Nobody was gonna go after anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.30,英文,,0,0,0,,And then it occurred to me, if you wanna find someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.97,英文,,0,0,0,,and the only thing you know about them is where they're gonna end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe let them get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:59.57,英文,,0,0,0,,I loved him too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:41.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start with names.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:45.65,英文,,0,0,0,,The dark-haired guy was Manny. The other guy was Owen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.49,英文,,0,0,0,,The girl with the dark hair and the bald one,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.36,英文,,0,0,0,,one of them's named Nora. I'm not sure which.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.70,英文,,0,0,0,,The girl with the braid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:52.91,英文,,0,0,0,,Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:54.83,英文,,0,0,0,,Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Where are they from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.67,英文,,0,0,0,,I saw a patch on a backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:05.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Yellow triangle, wolf's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.51,英文,,0,0,0,,and the letters W-L-F.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:12.22,英文,,0,0,0,,And then, I remembered a story Eugene told me from back when he was a Firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:13.89,英文,,0,0,0,,He said that there were these small regional groups
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.35,英文,,0,0,0,,in the West all trying to fight FEDRA,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:18.35,英文,,0,0,0,,and how stupid it was that they didn't just join together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:22.23,英文,,0,0,0,,One of those groups was the Washington Liberation Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Out of Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:28.36,英文,,0,0,0,,W-L-F. Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Fucking morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:33.16,英文,,0,0,0,,- Did he say how small they were? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:35.37,英文,,0,0,0,,But seeing as how no one's ever mentioned them since,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:37.58,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing small enough for us to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.04,英文,,0,0,0,,Who else knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.58,英文,,0,0,0,,Just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:47.17,英文,,0,0,0,,I wasn't gonna tell anyone before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:08.28,英文,,0,0,0,,So, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:22.96,英文,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.46,英文,,0,0,0,,I gotta think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.75,英文,,0,0,0,,Think about what? Let's fucking get these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Ellie, it ain't that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.43,英文,,0,0,0,,The town is still recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.59,英文,,0,0,0,,- So are you. - We get where you're coming from--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:36.30,英文,,0,0,0,,No, we don't get where you're coming from. I don't get where you're coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:38.01,英文,,0,0,0,,If it had been you, Joel would be halfway to Seattle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:39.93,英文,,0,0,0,,- before the sun came up. - He'd be halfway to Seattle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.31,英文,,0,0,0,,to save my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:43.94,英文,,0,0,0,,But when we lost people, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:46.06,英文,,0,0,0,,It would just break him like it was his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:47.52,英文,,0,0,0,,I saw that time and time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:49.32,英文,,0,0,0,,And don't talk to me like I didn't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.45,英文,,0,0,0,,He was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:18:00.70,英文,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm not sayin' you shouldn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.25,英文,,0,0,0,,But if we're gonna put a posse together,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:05.67,英文,,0,0,0,,we gotta do it right, which means taking it to Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.92,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's fuckin' necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:10.84,英文,,0,0,0,,She's gonna want a council meeting, open it up to the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:13.05,英文,,0,0,0,,Everyone who wants to get heard gets heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.68,英文,,0,0,0,,But you'll back us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Of course, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:22.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:31.65,英文,,0,0,0,,And you, you hold out information on me again,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:34.20,英文,,0,0,0,,you got rendering detail for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.45,英文,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.92,英文,,0,0,0,,We buried our dead ten miles south of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.30,英文,,0,0,0,,If you want to visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.97,英文,,0,0,0,,When we're on our way to Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:52.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:57.70,英文,,0,0,0,,"No one following. All clear. Keep moving."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:02.12,英文,,0,0,0,,Once we get resettled, I'll teach you to whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:07.54,英文,,0,0,0,,Why can't you tell me where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.71,英文,,0,0,0,,'Cause we don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.79,英文,,0,0,0,,I've told you the reason we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:16.88,英文,,0,0,0,,I know, but why can't she just keep us safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.26,英文,,0,0,0,,The Prophet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:23.47,英文,,0,0,0,,She's been dead ten years, Constance. I wouldn't count on her to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:26.27,英文,,0,0,0,,But Ezra said the Prophet is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:29.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, she is, in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:31.27,英文,,0,0,0,,A prophet isn't magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:34.86,英文,,0,0,0,,They're just people that see truths hidden from others
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:37.40,英文,,0,0,0,,and share that truth, no matter what the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.57,英文,,0,0,0,,So it was with our Prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.20,英文,,0,0,0,,So it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.58,英文,,0,0,0,,That's how we keep her spirit alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:49.71,英文,,0,0,0,,Follow her words, we obey her teachings, but we keep ourselves safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.67,英文,,0,0,0,,Then, can I have a hammer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.34,英文,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.39,英文,,0,0,0,,Tell me, you feel safer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:07.64,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:10.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Understand, what we're giving you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:15.36,英文,,0,0,0,,will keep you far, far safer than a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:19.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:21.86,英文,,0,0,0,,From home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.53,英文,,0,0,0,,From war.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:36.30,英文,,0,0,0,,Take cover! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:54.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:57.94,英文,,0,0,0,,Wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:02.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.11,英文,,0,0,0,,Good, but rotate. More.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:07.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, the right side. Just the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:08.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Come on, man, that side hurts more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:10.91,英文,,0,0,0,,I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:12.08,英文,,0,0,0,,- Come on. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:14.79,英文,,0,0,0,,Harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:16.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Harder! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:17.46,英文,,0,0,0,,Last five.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.47,英文,,0,0,0,,There it is, okay. Done for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.47,0:22:23.68,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:26.39,英文,,0,0,0,,So, what'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:27.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, for someone who sat on their ass
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:30.35,英文,,0,0,0,,for three months, I'm pleasantly surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:32.31,英文,,0,0,0,,- Yeah? - Push-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:34.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and crunches when they weren't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.44,0:22:36.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.31,0:22:38.65,英文,,0,0,0,,A few more weeks, and you'll be right back to where you were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:40.27,英文,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:42.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Which is 80% of where you should have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:44.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:50.49,英文,,0,0,0,,So, I heard you're on the council now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:52.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:55.33,英文,,0,0,0,,So, you know about the meeting coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:58.29,英文,,0,0,0,,I know about the meeting coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.38,0:23:02.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:05.80,英文,,0,0,0,,I can't discuss upcoming votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:07.93,英文,,0,0,0,,Seriously? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:09.18,英文,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:10.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Dude, you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.97,0:23:12.47,英文,,0,0,0,,I know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:14.52,英文,,0,0,0,,Gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:17.52,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:20.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:23.94,英文,,0,0,0,,The council won't make up their mind until we hear people speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.94,0:23:25.99,英文,,0,0,0,,So, here's a little advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:28.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Organize your thoughts, write them down,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:30.12,英文,,0,0,0,,and then read 'em out loud tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.12,0:23:31.87,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah, 'cause I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:33.87,英文,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're angry, Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.92,英文,,0,0,0,,And no one's gonna vote for angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:47.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Which is why I keep saying we need to invest
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.26,0:23:50.05,英文,,0,0,0,,more in turkeys and less in chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:53.31,英文,,0,0,0,,And that brings me back to my earlier point about corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:55.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Corn, some of you have heard me say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.48,0:23:59.23,英文,,0,0,0,,is not the easiest crop to grow, but it is among the fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.23,0:24:02.15,英文,,0,0,0,,You can plot a graph that shows ease and resources
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:04.02,英文,,0,0,0,,versus time to harvest and get a li--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:07.53,英文,,0,0,0,,Scott, I'm sorry, but we gotta keep you on target here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:11.03,英文,,0,0,0,,But it's an open meeting. The bylaws say that--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.03,0:24:12.58,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should stick to what everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.58,0:24:14.20,英文,,0,0,0,,came here to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.79,0:24:17.20,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't really have an opinion on the Seattle thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.21,0:24:19.12,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:21.38,英文,,0,0,0,,So, that was Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.25,0:24:23.67,英文,,0,0,0,,Next is Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.67,0:24:27.01,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Joel meant so much to so many of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.01,0:24:28.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.97,0:24:31.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Can you take him, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.14,0:24:33.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.85,0:24:43.65,英文,,0,0,0,,I said that Joel meant so much to so many of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.82,0:24:46.07,英文,,0,0,0,,But he wasn't the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.32,0:24:49.11,英文,,0,0,0,,I lost my sister that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.11,0:24:52.24,英文,,0,0,0,,A lot of people in here buried family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.82,0:24:55.66,英文,,0,0,0,,And now, you wanna send, what, you're saying 16 of our best?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.75,0:25:00.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, while they're gone, who's gonna be on the wall if Raiders come?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.25,0:25:02.71,英文,,0,0,0,,A wall that's barely mended.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.71,0:25:05.88,英文,,0,0,0,,And none of you up there can promise us that all 16 will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.51,0:25:10.55,英文,,0,0,0,,So, my heart is with you, Tommy and Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.55,0:25:13.89,英文,,0,0,0,,We are too hurt, and it is too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.14,0:25:16.56,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.73,0:25:22.19,英文,,0,0,0,,Next is Carlisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.65,0:25:29.86,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll be quick. 'Cause this one's simple to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.86,0:25:33.78,英文,,0,0,0,,People came and killed Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.95,0:25:37.33,英文,,0,0,0,,So, why wouldn't we wanna take our vengeance?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.33,0:25:41.12,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, because we're not supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.87,0:25:45.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Forgive and be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.13,0:25:48.71,英文,,0,0,0,,No grudges. No revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.30,0:25:50.84,英文,,0,0,0,,And I'm not even a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.26,0:25:53.68,英文,,0,0,0,,I've always seen the wisdom in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.68,0:25:58.10,英文,,0,0,0,,That's what separates us from the Raiders and the murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.18,0:26:00.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Our capacity for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.98,0:26:04.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Those sons of bitches don't deserve our mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.52,0:26:06.98,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, of course they don't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.98,0:26:09.36,英文,,0,0,0,,- That's what makes it mercy. - Well, to hell with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.40,0:26:12.15,英文,,0,0,0,,And to hell with you for saying it, Carlisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.15,0:26:13.32,英文,,0,0,0,,- Seth, sit down. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.32,0:26:15.41,英文,,0,0,0,,- You're not on the list. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.41,0:26:17.53,英文,,0,0,0,,What the hell are we all talking about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.62,0:26:21.12,英文,,0,0,0,,It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.12,0:26:23.12,英文,,0,0,0,,What, we gotta forgive everybody when they show up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.12,0:26:25.08,英文,,0,0,0,,and piss in our eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.08,0:26:26.88,英文,,0,0,0,,They came into our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.46,0:26:29.30,英文,,0,0,0,,They took one of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.05,0:26:34.76,英文,,0,0,0,,My God, somebody shoots your brother, you wanna take the locks off your doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.76,0:26:35.89,英文,,0,0,0,,Grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.64,0:26:38.76,英文,,0,0,0,,You idiots, they'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.60,0:26:42.31,英文,,0,0,0,,They'll come back because we didn't make 'em pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.02,0:26:45.40,英文,,0,0,0,,And when they come back, they'll be laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.61,0:26:49.15,英文,,0,0,0,,And you'll all deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.53,0:26:53.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Bunch of goddamn victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.50,0:27:09.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.36,0:27:31.32,英文,,0,0,0,,I normally don't write things down
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.32,0:27:33.78,英文,,0,0,0,,because I normally don't think before I talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.78,0:27:36.82,英文,,0,0,0,,which has gotten me in trouble before, a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.82,0:27:40.24,英文,,0,0,0,,and it's cost me in ways that sometimes couldn't be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.08,0:27:45.58,英文,,0,0,0,,But I can't afford that right now, because I know what I'm asking is a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs12}{\fn黑体}外挂字幕由 {\c&H003CA8DC&}美剧迷 / www.mjmtv.top{\c&HFFFFFF&} 合并官方中英双语
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.37,0:27:49.25,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm asking us to risk more people and resources,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.25,0:27:51.29,英文,,0,0,0,,and at the worst possible time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.29,0:27:55.46,英文,,0,0,0,,And I want everyone to know, it's not because I want revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.47,0:27:57.84,英文,,0,0,0,,It's not. It's not about revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.84,0:28:00.72,英文,,0,0,0,,What I want is what you used to give people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.81,0:28:03.31,英文,,0,0,0,,I want justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.64,0:28:08.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Because it's either that, or we do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.06,0:28:11.15,英文,,0,0,0,,That's what everyone else out there is going to do for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.15,0:28:12.52,英文,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.52,0:28:15.28,英文,,0,0,0,,A whole world of people who won't lift a finger
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.28,0:28:18.20,英文,,0,0,0,,if something bad happens to me or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.78,0:28:21.57,英文,,0,0,0,,We have a word for these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.37,0:28:24.16,英文,,0,0,0,,They're called strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.16,0:28:27.00,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think that we're strangers to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.00,0:28:29.50,英文,,0,0,0,,And I want to know that I can count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.50,0:28:31.79,英文,,0,0,0,,And I swear, if someone hurts any of you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.79,0:28:35.00,英文,,0,0,0,,or the people you love, you can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.63,0:28:37.63,英文,,0,0,0,,That's what holds all this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.80,0:28:41.34,英文,,0,0,0,,Not potluck dinners or New Year's Eve dances.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.35,0:28:45.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Definitely not a wall, because that thing got busted through.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.06,0:28:46.98,英文,,0,0,0,,But Jackson is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.31,0:28:52.40,英文,,0,0,0,,I'll accept whatever the council decides.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.40,0:28:55.57,英文,,0,0,0,,But I am asking you, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.90,0:28:59.61,英文,,0,0,0,,do what it takes to see that justice is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.32,0:29:04.58,英文,,0,0,0,,Not for me. Not even for Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.83,0:29:10.87,英文,,0,0,0,,I am asking you, please, do it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.80,0:29:16.96,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.39,0:29:31.35,英文,,0,0,0,,The council will now vote on the proposal to send a party of 16 citizens to Seattle
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.35,0:29:34.94,英文,,0,0,0,,to find the people who killed Joel and execute them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.42,0:29:59.05,英文,,0,0,0,,Amy-Beth?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.26,0:30:04.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.26,0:30:07.26,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.97,0:30:10.10,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.48,0:30:13.60,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.27,0:30:16.27,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.86,0:30:18.86,英文,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.57,0:30:21.61,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.91,0:30:24.95,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.37,0:30:27.49,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.95,0:30:29.99,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.08,0:30:33.33,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.17,0:30:39.92,英文,,0,0,0,,The vote is 8 to 3. The proposal is rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.68,0:30:47.18,英文,,0,0,0,,Adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.29,0:31:14.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Here we go, nine. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.96,0:31:17.96,英文,,0,0,0,,Grab the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.04,0:31:20.30,英文,,0,0,0,,Attaboy, nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.42,0:31:23.84,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.84,0:31:25.72,英文,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.51,0:31:29.14,英文,,0,0,0,,Hell, yeah! I had Tigers season tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.14,0:31:30.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Get in the game, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.47,0:31:33.31,英文,,0,0,0,,This actually isn't that far off from the '03 squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.31,0:31:35.48,英文,,0,0,0,,Louie, stand up! Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.48,0:31:38.69,英文,,0,0,0,,You want a beer? I get them from Marshall.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.66,0:31:54.04,英文,,0,0,0,,I spotted you in the crowd at the meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.37,0:31:56.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.62,0:31:59.88,英文,,0,0,0,,And I thought to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.88,0:32:02.42,英文,,0,0,0,,she's probably been extra busy these last few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.42,0:32:04.80,英文,,0,0,0,,Brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.80,0:32:08.55,英文,,0,0,0,,And I'm supposed to see a shrink myself, you know, to process it all, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.14,0:32:10.14,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.97,0:32:14.22,英文,,0,0,0,,- So, what do you do, then? - Oh, well, I'm an alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.22,0:32:16.64,英文,,0,0,0,,And I smoke as much weed as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.64,0:32:18.44,英文,,0,0,0,,You know, complete fuckin' disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.48,0:32:21.56,英文,,0,0,0,,But you're not here 'cause you're worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.98,0:32:24.61,英文,,0,0,0,,Two outs, guys, two outs. Look alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.61,0:32:25.82,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.61,0:32:30.07,英文,,0,0,0,,You see things that others don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.16,0:32:35.04,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm nervous she's gonna do somethin' stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.04,0:32:36.87,英文,,0,0,0,,What, you didn't believe her speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.87,0:32:39.54,英文,,0,0,0,,- Did you? - Course not. She's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.46,0:32:42.67,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a difference between lyin' and being a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.67,0:32:45.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know. And that one? Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.09,0:32:49.26,英文,,0,0,0,,There was maybe one person she told the truth to, and he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.84,0:32:53.68,英文,,0,0,0,,But we can agree to disagree about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.39,0:32:59.64,英文,,0,0,0,,What matters is you're afraid. So, let's talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.64,0:33:02.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay. Free of charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.19,0:33:08.44,英文,,0,0,0,,I just don't want her to go down the same paths that Joel did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.41,0:33:13.74,英文,,0,0,0,,Comin' up with justifications and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.87,0:33:18.25,英文,,0,0,0,,All he was really doin' was lashin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.83,0:33:21.83,英文,,0,0,0,,So, you think she might have learned that behavior from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.09,0:33:25.59,英文,,0,0,0,,There it is! Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.59,0:33:27.92,英文,,0,0,0,,Turns out nurture can only do this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.55,0:33:30.51,英文,,0,0,0,,The rest is nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.51,0:33:33.18,英文,,0,0,0,,If she's on a path, it's not one that Joel put her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.47,0:33:36.05,英文,,0,0,0,,No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.06,0:33:39.60,英文,,0,0,0,,I think they were walking side by side from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.98,0:33:44.23,英文,,0,0,0,,Tommy, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.19,0:33:48.15,英文,,0,0,0,,You inherited her, and you wanna keep her out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.15,0:33:50.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Take it from a psychotherapist of 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.99,0:33:53.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Some people just...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.49,0:33:59.83,英文,,0,0,0,,Some people just can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.27,0:34:30.57,英文,,0,0,0,,- Who is it? - Dina.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.49,0:34:35.49,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.08,0:34:39.79,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.79,0:34:43.00,英文,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think that is where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.63,0:34:51.46,英文,,0,0,0,,- Are you alone? - I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.01,0:35:01.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.31,0:35:03.73,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.73,0:35:05.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Please don't try and talk me out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.31,0:35:06.90,英文,,0,0,0,,You think that's why I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.94,0:35:10.73,英文,,0,0,0,,So, what's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.24,0:35:14.15,英文,,0,0,0,,Go to Seattle and kill Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.65,0:35:15.70,英文,,0,0,0,,What route?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.03,0:35:18.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.20,0:35:21.66,英文,,0,0,0,,And is that all guns, or do you have medical supplies in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.66,0:35:22.75,英文,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.04,0:35:26.50,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, better not land weird on an ankle
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.50,0:35:30.00,英文,,0,0,0,,or get a fever on your well-charted path "northwest."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.00,0:35:31.96,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay, so what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.59,0:35:41.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Stay off the highways. Steer clear of cities or settlements.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.51,0:35:43.56,英文,,0,0,0,,First stage is through the national forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.56,0:35:46.94,英文,,0,0,0,,Once we're out, we follow the Snake River Canyon,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.94,0:35:48.52,英文,,0,0,0,,then break off through the Snoqualmie Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.52,0:35:49.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Snoqualmie?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.90,0:35:52.44,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Snoqualmie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.44,0:35:55.82,英文,,0,0,0,,Approach Seattle from the east, then reassess based on what we find.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.82,0:35:58.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Provisions. Travel light, but smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.57,0:36:00.62,英文,,0,0,0,,Winter coats for beds, jackets for blankets.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.62,0:36:02.95,英文,,0,0,0,,First aid kits, batteries, bear spray.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.95,0:36:04.95,英文,,0,0,0,,Now, handguns. What are you bringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.17,0:36:09.04,英文,,0,0,0,,- Is that Joel's? - Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.63,0:36:12.21,英文,,0,0,0,,So, that's what you're gonna kill her with?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.21,0:36:14.34,英文,,0,0,0,,- Fuckin' right. - Then, save it for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.34,0:36:15.84,英文,,0,0,0,,It's slow and kicks like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.22,0:36:20.89,英文,,0,0,0,,Really? Shoot your damn ass off?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.68,0:36:23.35,英文,,0,0,0,,I've heard that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.35,0:36:25.85,英文,,0,0,0,,We'll want at least 100 shells apiece, plus 50 rifle rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.85,0:36:28.39,英文,,0,0,0,,Bring any long gun you want, as long as it's scoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.39,0:36:31.23,英文,,0,0,0,,Chlorine tablets, a pan, and something to keep Shimmer dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.23,0:36:32.90,英文,,0,0,0,,- Just Shimmer? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.90,0:36:34.73,英文,,0,0,0,,We share a horse. Fewer resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.73,0:36:38.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Everything else is what you'd figure, except this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.82,0:36:40.87,英文,,0,0,0,,Boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.82,0:36:44.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Love the Converse. Respect your consistency.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.37,0:36:46.58,英文,,0,0,0,,But you're not crossing open country in fuckin' Chucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.58,0:36:48.96,英文,,0,0,0,,- I've done it before. - No Chucks. Questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.96,0:36:51.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, one. How the fuck are we gonna get all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.63,0:36:52.96,英文,,0,0,0,,I know a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.96,0:36:56.59,英文,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. No, don't tell me you told Jesse, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.59,0:36:58.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Captain Wyoming? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.88,0:37:02.22,英文,,0,0,0,,I love the man, but he's a little uptight about rules and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.76,0:37:04.51,英文,,0,0,0,,Wear all the clothes you're gonna bring,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.51,0:37:06.01,英文,,0,0,0,,fill your pockets with ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.02,0:37:09.27,英文,,0,0,0,,Everything else needs to fit inside a holster or your backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.27,0:37:12.36,英文,,0,0,0,,We'll meet by the old east gate, 3:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.06,0:37:14.07,英文,,0,0,0,,3:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.69,0:37:16.78,英文,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.82,0:37:21.07,英文,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.45,0:37:25.83,英文,,0,0,0,,You know, you could have just asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.83,0:37:27.95,英文,,0,0,0,,No, I actually didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.79,0:37:32.12,英文,,0,0,0,,Now you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.04,0:38:10.41,英文,,0,0,0,,Trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.25,0:38:14.13,英文,,0,0,0,,It's better. Trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.35,0:38:34.31,英文,,0,0,0,,How'd you get her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.31,0:38:36.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Jeanine's night watch at the stables.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.61,0:38:38.69,英文,,0,0,0,,She's sympathetic to our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.69,0:38:39.98,英文,,0,0,0,,"Our cause"?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.98,0:38:42.57,英文,,0,0,0,,You're the one that gave the "us" speech, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.66,0:38:47.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Saddlebags are filled with stuff I had squirreled away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.37,0:38:49.37,英文,,0,0,0,,Two weeks' worth of hardtack, bandages,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.37,0:38:51.45,英文,,0,0,0,,alcohol, meds, batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.45,0:38:53.79,英文,,0,0,0,,I'd come with you, but I caught some friendly fire on New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.50,0:38:56.63,英文,,0,0,0,,- You sure it was friendly? - Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.17,0:38:59.21,英文,,0,0,0,,We got ten minutes before a patrol comes by.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.21,0:39:01.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's get you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.32,0:42:56.03,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.66,0:42:57.66,英文,,0,0,0,,F.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.24,0:42:59.24,英文,,0,0,0,,F.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.00,0:43:03.62,英文,,0,0,0,,- Fleetwood Mac. - Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.62,0:43:04.79,英文,,0,0,0,,What? What do you mean, "no"?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.79,0:43:06.54,英文,,0,0,0,,- It's my opinion. - Yeah, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.54,0:43:09.80,英文,,0,0,0,,your opinion is wrong because Frank Zappa exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.01,0:43:14.38,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay, so, G.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.09,0:43:16.13,英文,,0,0,0,,Green Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.14,0:43:18.43,英文,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong. It's Guns N' Roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.60,0:43:25.06,英文,,0,0,0,,Ozzy Osbourne.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.06,0:43:27.31,英文,,0,0,0,,Nice! Double points.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.31,0:43:30.82,英文,,0,0,0,,So, L-M-N-O, P.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.82,0:43:33.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously gonna make me do the entire alphabet?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.99,0:43:36.53,英文,,0,0,0,,We don't have to. I'm incredibly flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.66,0:43:39.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Lemme see, new topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.20,0:43:41.28,英文,,0,0,0,,- Or silence. - Got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.29,0:43:42.74,英文,,0,0,0,,First person you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.75,0:43:44.20,英文,,0,0,0,,Jesus, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.20,0:43:46.12,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, fun stories of childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.67,0:43:50.96,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, the first one's too fucked up, but I can tell you the second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.96,0:43:52.05,英文,,0,0,0,,I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.63,0:43:56.09,英文,,0,0,0,,It was a little before Joel and I got to Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.09,0:44:01.06,英文,,0,0,0,,In Kansas City, he got jumped by this kid, maybe just a couple years older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.06,0:44:06.44,英文,,0,0,0,,And I came up behind him, raised my gun and, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.81,0:44:09.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.81,0:44:13.03,英文,,0,0,0,,Interesting. I shoot a guy, and you feel sorry for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.03,0:44:16.32,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm just loyal like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.70,0:44:19.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Let me know if you see any outcroppings
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.37,0:44:21.37,英文,,0,0,0,,- or spots with cover. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.37,0:44:22.95,英文,,0,0,0,,It looks okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.88,0:44:32.63,英文,,0,0,0,,Holy shit, that came on fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.63,0:44:35.00,英文,,0,0,0,,How the fuck did you know that was gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.01,0:44:37.26,英文,,0,0,0,,- I'm a witch. - Clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.62,0:45:04.12,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.12,0:45:06.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.59,0:45:24.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay, but I have a stupid question.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.10,0:45:35.48,英文,,0,0,0,,It's about New Year's Eve, and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.61,0:45:38.03,英文,,0,0,0,,the kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.20,0:45:42.57,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.57,0:45:45.45,英文,,0,0,0,,I mean, whatever, you were super high.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.45,0:45:47.16,英文,,0,0,0,,And you were drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.16,0:45:48.66,英文,,0,0,0,,Right, so it doesn't mean anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.66,0:45:50.79,英文,,0,0,0,,- if that's what you're asking. - No, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.62,0:45:52.92,英文,,0,0,0,,My question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.67,0:45:56.88,英文,,0,0,0,,how would you rate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.09,0:46:00.97,英文,,0,0,0,,- Scale of one to ten. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.97,0:46:03.26,英文,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.26,0:46:07.01,英文,,0,0,0,,You've kissed girls before. You're gay, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.64,0:46:10.48,英文,,0,0,0,,I'm just curious. I wanna know if I'm any good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.44,0:46:12.98,英文,,0,0,0,,One to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.73,0:46:17.32,英文,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine. Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.32,0:46:18.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Fuck you, "six."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.69,0:46:21.78,英文,,0,0,0,,- That's not bad. - That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.78,0:46:23.24,英文,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.24,0:46:25.07,英文,,0,0,0,,For the record, I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.37,0:46:29.33,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, you asked, and I told you. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.54,0:46:33.46,英文,,0,0,0,,You can go back to Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.46,0:46:34.92,英文,,0,0,0,,I already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.88,0:46:37.88,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.14,0:46:51.02,英文,,0,0,0,,Does he ever strike you as sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.14,0:46:53.89,英文,,0,0,0,,Jesse? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.31,0:46:57.90,英文,,0,0,0,,Has he ever told you why?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.32,0:47:00.32,英文,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.53,0:47:05.99,英文,,0,0,0,,But I think deep inside, that's just how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.79,0:47:12.75,英文,,0,0,0,,- At least, I hope that's why. - Why would you hope that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.75,0:47:19.67,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, because if it's not that,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.38,0:47:22.67,英文,,0,0,0,,then it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.55,0:47:29.47,英文,,0,0,0,,Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.47,0:47:31.60,英文,,0,0,0,,Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.48,0:47:42.61,英文,,0,0,0,,Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.82,0:47:46.61,英文,,0,0,0,,I wasn't that high.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.71,0:48:02.25,英文,,0,0,0,,- How much further? - Close.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.42,0:48:05.59,英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe ten miles?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.59,0:48:09.43,英文,,0,0,0,,In theory, we'll come out near Highway Five, just north of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.66,0:48:30.07,英文,,0,0,0,,He was running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.12,0:48:34.24,英文,,0,0,0,,What's that symbol?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.24,0:48:36.25,英文,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I've never seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.59,0:48:51.64,英文,,0,0,0,,A lot of different calibers. I don't think this was FEDRA.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.76,0:48:54.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Dina.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.56,0:48:57.85,英文,,0,0,0,,Dina?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.10,0:49:00.35,英文,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.69,0:49:07.69,英文,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.57,0:49:09.57,英文,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.17,0:50:06.25,英文,,0,0,0,,Doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.76,0:50:12.22,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sorry, it's just that's never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.80,0:50:14.97,英文,,0,0,0,,I think it was the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.97,0:50:16.64,英文,,0,0,0,,It wasn't easy to look at either.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.18,0:50:22.19,英文,,0,0,0,,If this was fucking them,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.77,0:50:24.65,英文,,0,0,0,,if Abby and her crew did this to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.81,0:50:27.19,英文,,0,0,0,,to kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.15,0:50:32.36,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.12,0:50:37.28,英文,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.77,0:51:09.19,英文,,0,0,0,,We're close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.97,0:51:40.43,英文,,0,0,0,,It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.43,0:51:42.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Too quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.31,0:51:47.27,英文,,0,0,0,,- Curtis or Viper? - Both, in all four movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.77,0:51:52.40,英文,,0,0,0,,Nine more miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.15,0:51:55.45,英文,,0,0,0,,Nine more.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.59,0:52:21.97,英文,,0,0,0,,Fucking Seattle. Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.93,0:52:26.69,英文,,0,0,0,,Plus, no one's shooting at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.36,0:52:32.11,英文,,0,0,0,,I guess there aren't that many Wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.40,0:52:35.36,英文,,0,0,0,,There's about to be a whole lot less.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.82,0:52:38.99,英文,,0,0,0,,Curtis or Viper?
